/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_0.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I offer it to you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1000.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And say, have they not risen?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10001.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then with a curse he hurled the little axe at him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10005.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then he stood for a while watching,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10007.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But that was not his desire;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10009.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then with a roar he leaped forward,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10012.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as light leaps from a cloud,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10014.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and something swept past him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10017.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and all saw that he was dead,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10019.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|crying,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1002.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as vultures gather round a dying ox?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10020.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|having conquered the chief of the People of the Axe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10022.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"That is our law indeed, stranger,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10025.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but this also is our law:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10027.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that now you must do battle, one by one, with all who come against you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10033.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I have nothing to say against the rule,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10035.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for their hearts were mad with wrath because of the death of their father and because the chieftainship had gone from their race,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10044.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that in truth they cared little if they lived or died.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10048.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But there were none besides these,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1005.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they will come true,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10050.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now if I must fight all these one by one,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10053.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If I find one other to stand beside me in the fray,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10056.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and all of you come on at once against us twain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10059.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|ten against two,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1006.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and mine is the song of a people that is doomed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10060.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to slay us or be slain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10062.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|will that be to your minds?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10064.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The brethren consulted together,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10066.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and held that so they should be in better case than if they went up one by one.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10072.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as he fled round and round,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10074.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and knew that he hungered to share the fight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10077.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So he called aloud that he whom he should choose,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1008.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But of these other words I will speak in their place.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10080.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and who would stand back to back with him in the fray,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10084.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|should be the first after him among the People of the Axe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10088.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he walked slowly down the line scanning the faces of all,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10093.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till he came to where Galazi stood leaning on the Watcher.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10097.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Here is a great fellow who bears a great club,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10100.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"How are you named, fellow?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10101.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I am named Wolf,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10102.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|are you willing to stand back to back with me in this fray of two against ten?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10107.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yet,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10108.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because you have shown yourself a warrior of might,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1011.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went to my mother.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10110.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to taste again of the joy of battle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10113.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will stand back to back with you,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10115.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and see this matter ended.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10117.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"A bargain, Wolf!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10118.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|All there looked on them wondering,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10120.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I think that few can stand before them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10123.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Some shall find it so,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10125.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|victory is good, but death ends all and is best of all.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10129.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and at the point on its hammer,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1013.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently she raised herself from the ground and sat up with her hands over her face.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10131.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|balancing it in his hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10133.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|its curved blade being inwards towards his breast,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10137.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the hollow point turned towards the foe.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10140.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They were all great men, made fierce with rage and shame.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10145.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Yet there is virtue in the axe,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10147.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the other,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10148.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and for the club, it seems that I know it:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10150.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I think it is named Watcher of the Fords,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10153.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I myself have seen him aloft when I was young;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10156.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They are but lads, indeed, yet they have drunk wolf's milk.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10160.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Meanwhile, an aged man drew near to speak the word of onset;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10165.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He must give the signal by throwing up a spear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10168.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and when it struck the ground,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1017.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The blood from the wound the stick had made ran down her face on to her breast,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10170.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The old man took the spear and threw it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10173.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but his hand was weak,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10174.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he cast so clumsily that it fell among the sons of Jikiza,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10179.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|causing them to open up to let it pass between them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10183.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and drawing the eyes of all ten of them to it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10186.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|being careless where it touched.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10188.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as men had thought they must,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10190.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|sprang forward,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10191.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|each at the line of foes who were before him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10194.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|While the ten still stood confused,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10197.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for it had been their plan to attack,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10199.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and yet a man dropped dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_102.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There he was thrown in with men who,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10201.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The Watcher also was up,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10203.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he fell like a falling tree,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10206.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and was the death of one.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10207.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Through the lines of the ten passed the Wolf-Brethren in the gaps that each had made.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1021.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She sat for a long while thus,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10213.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then they turned swiftly and charged towards each other again;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10217.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but before them lay four men dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10220.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The onslaught and the return were so swift,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10223.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that men scarcely understood what had been done;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10226.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|With a shout of rage they rushed upon the pair from both sides,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1023.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while the child cried,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10230.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but in either case one was the most eager,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10234.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and outstepped the other two,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10236.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|before his fellows were at his side.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10238.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he was not to be caught thus,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10240.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for he bent his middle sideways,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and as he bent tapped with the point of the axe at the head of the smiter,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10248.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|dealing death on him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10249.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|or the Slaughterer,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1025.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the cow lowed to be milked,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10251.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he who came at Galazi the Wolf rushed on wildly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10255.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|holding his spear short.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10257.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But Galazi was cunning in war.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10259.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He took one step forward to meet him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1026.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I wiped up the blood with the grass.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10262.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|swinging the Watcher backward,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10264.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but the shield was to the Watcher what a leaf is to the wind.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10268.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Full on its hide the huge club fell, making a loud sound;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10273.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the war-shield doubled up like a raw skin,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10276.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he who bore it fell crushed to the earth.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10280.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but never coming within reach of axe or club.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10283.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|yet its head flew on,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10285.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for his hands were empty,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10286.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the others followed swiftly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10288.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for the heart was out of them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1029.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At last she took her hands away and spoke to me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10290.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and they dared to do battle with these two no more.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10293.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Thus the fight was ended,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10295.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and from its beginning till the finish was not longer than the time in which men might count a hundred slowly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10303.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Ah, that was a cunning fight!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10305.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you sons of the Unconquered, who run so fast, stay your feet.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10309.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I give you peace;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1031.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she said,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10311.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the fighting is done,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10312.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so let us to the chief's hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10314.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he turned and went with Galazi,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10316.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and after him followed all the people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10319.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He thanked her;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1032.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I have dreamed a dream.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10320.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and this was deeper,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10322.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as he would have no woman meddling with his wounds.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10325.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he hated Zinita most of them all.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10329.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who sat before him with a frightened face,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1033.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he was grown like a giant.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10331.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|saying,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10332.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and against her will,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10333.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|persecuting her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10335.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I had intended to kill you as an offering to her anger,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10338.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but there has been enough blood-letting to-day.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10341.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whom I myself will take in marriage:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10343.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you shall give a hundred head of cattle.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10346.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then get you gone from among the People of the Axe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10349.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So Masilo rose up and went,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1035.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his eyes blazed like the lightning,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10351.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and his face was green with fear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10354.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Zinita watched him go,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10356.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and she was glad of it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10357.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and because the Slaughterer had named her for his wife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10361.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I am well rid of Masilo,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10363.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she said aloud, in the hearing of Galazi,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10366.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I had been better pleased to see him dead before me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1037.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He caught up people after people in his hands and tore them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10370.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"This woman has a fierce heart,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10372.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|doing homage to him as chief and holder of the axe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10375.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and also they did homage to the axe itself.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10379.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and their number was many,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10380.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he grew great and fat in cattle and wives,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10384.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a man ventured to stand up before him in fight,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10387.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but none could conquer him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10389.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but dwelt with them little,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10391.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as of old,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10392.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he swept at night across the forest and the plains,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10395.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the howling of the ghost-wolves went with him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10399.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he slept at the side of Zinita,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for thirty or forty years,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10401.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and she loved him much and bore him children.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10405.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Pick-out-the-old-men,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10407.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|had stood before the king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10408.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the Great Mother Elephant,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1041.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Before him was the green of summer,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10410.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Mother of the Heavens,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10411.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and because all could not be found,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10414.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|some of the bones of my wives were collected also to make up the number.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10419.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When all were brought together,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10421.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a great pit was dug and the bones were set out in order in the pit and buried;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10427.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but not alone,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10429.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and these maidens were covered over with the earth,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1043.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I saw our people, Mopo;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10432.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Moreover,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10433.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|all those who were present at the burial were made into a regiment and commanded that they should dwell by the grave for the space of a year.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10442.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that the milk of the cows should be spilled upon the ground,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10445.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that no woman should give birth to a child for a full year,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10449.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that if any should dare to bear children,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1045.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they were many and fat,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10452.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10453.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and great sorrow came upon the land.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10456.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then for a little while there was quiet,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10458.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he wept often,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1046.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|their hearts laughed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10460.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we who waited on him wept also as we walked,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10464.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till at length it came about by use that we could weep without ceasing for many hours.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10470.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|No angry woman can weep as we wept in those days;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10474.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for the teaching of which I received many cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10477.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for woe to him who had no tears in those days.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1048.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the men were brave,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10481.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though he said nothing more to me of this matter,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10483.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|None of them ever came back again.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10486.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|In after days it was reported to the king that these soldiers were missing,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1049.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the girls were fair;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10491.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|never having returned,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10492.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he only laughed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10494.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|son of Mopo,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10495.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|was a fierce one,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10496.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and had eaten them also.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10498.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that dreadful night to be followed by a more dreadful morrow.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1050.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I counted their children by the hundreds.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10503.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he put his arm about my neck and groaned and wept for his mother,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10508.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whom he had murdered,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10509.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I groaned also,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10511.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I did not weep,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10512.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because it was dark,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10514.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Therefore, I spared my tears, lest they should fail me in my need.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10519.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as they came in thousands and tens of thousands,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1052.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I saw them again, Mopo.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10523.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till it seemed as though the whole world were mourning,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10526.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|None might cease their crying,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10528.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and none dared to drink so much as a cup of water.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10532.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Come, let us go forth, Mopo, and look on those who mourn with us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10537.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we went out,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10538.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and after us came men armed with clubs to do the bidding of the king.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1054.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thousands of bones tumbled together in a rocky place,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10543.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|On every side the land was black with them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10546.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When they saw the king they ceased from their howling and sang the war-song,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10552.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then once again they howled,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10554.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10555.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the sight became dreadful,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10557.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as the sun rose higher the day grew hot,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10560.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and utter weariness came upon the people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10563.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who were packed together like herds of cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10566.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they might neither eat nor drink.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10568.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and were trampled to death,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10570.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|their tongues hanging from their jaws,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10573.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we shall learn who are the wizards that have brought these ills upon us,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10577.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10578.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and with him were his wives and followers.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1058.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10581.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|This man could weep no more; he gasped with thirst and heat.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10586.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The king looked at him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10588.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"See, Mopo,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10589.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|see that brute who has no tears for my mother who is dead!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1059.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|stood over the bones and laughed till the earth shook.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10594.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Shall such as he live to look upon the sun,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10597.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while I and thou must weep,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10599.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Take him away, and all those who are with him!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_106.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|had been intimately acquainted with the Zulu people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10602.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Take them away,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10603.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who do not weep because my mother is dead by witchcraft!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10607.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I followed also weeping,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10609.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the slayers also must weep as they slew.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10613.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently we came upon another man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10615.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|seeing the king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10616.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|took snuff secretly to bring tears to his eyes.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1062.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You alone were left of our people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10620.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Look at him, Mopo,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10622.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|look at the wizard who has no tears,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10624.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though my mother is dead by witchcraft.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10627.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he takes snuff to bring tears to his eyes that are dry with wickedness.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10633.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Oh, take him away!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10634.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So this one also was killed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10637.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and these were but the first of thousands,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1064.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and with you came others,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10640.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with fury,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10641.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and with the lust of blood.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10643.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He walked to and fro,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10645.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I with him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10646.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for he said that we who sorrowed must have food.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10649.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who do not weep because my mother is dead,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1065.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You stabbed him with a little spear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10652.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and those who chanced to stand before his arm were killed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10657.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till at length the slayers could slay no more,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10661.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and themselves were slain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10663.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because their strength had failed them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10665.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and they had no more tears.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10667.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And I also, I must slay, lest if I slew not I should myself be slain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1067.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he fell down and grew small again;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10675.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the people also went mad with their thirst and the fury of their fear.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10680.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They fell upon each other, killing each other;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10683.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|every man who had a foe sought him out and killed him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10687.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|None were spared, the place was but a shambles;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10691.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|there on that day died full seven thousand men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10695.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Take them away, the heartless brutes, take them away!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10699.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1070.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he fell down and cursed you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10700.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|there was cunning in his cruelty,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10702.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|also he slew on this day all those whom he hated or whom he feared.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10709.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At length the night came down,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10711.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the sun sank red that day,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10714.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|all the sky was like blood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10716.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and blood was all the earth beneath.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10719.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then the killing ceased,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1072.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|your sister-and he died.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10720.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because none had now the strength to kill,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10723.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the people lay panting in heaps upon the ground,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10726.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the living and the dead together.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10729.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I looked at them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10730.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and saw that if they were not allowed to eat and drink,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10733.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|before day dawned again the most of them would be dead,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10738.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I spoke to the king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10739.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I cared little in that hour if I lived or died;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1074.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we rose and went home.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10743.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|even my hope of vengeance was forgotten in the sickness of my heart.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10747.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a merry mourning for true-hearted men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10750.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thy sorrows and mine also.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10753.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Not so, Mopo,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10754.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10756.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|this is but the beginning;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10757.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|To-morrow, O King, few will be left to mourn;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1076.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I held my peace, for I was afraid, very much afraid.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10760.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But a few have perished of all the thousands who are gathered together.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10765.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Number the people and they will not be missed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10767.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yet hunger and thirst shall finish the spear's work.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10771.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The people have neither eaten nor drunk for a day and a night,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10774.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Look without, Black One, there they lie in heaps with the dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10779.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he saw that the work would go too far,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10782.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"It is hard, Mopo,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10784.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he said,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10785.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because of the gentleness of my heart,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10787.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will deal gently with them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10789.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Go out,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10790.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and bid my children eat and drink if they have the heart,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10793.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|sleep well,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_10794.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because of the gentleness of my heart,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1081.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and died quickly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1083.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then my mother fell down and died,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1085.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I cried very much,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1087.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I loved her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1088.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and it was dreadful to see her cold and stiff,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_109.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with their history,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1091.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with not a word to say however loudly I called to her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1095.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Well, they buried my mother, and she was soon forgotten.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1099.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I only remembered her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_11.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a song has been sung in my ears of how first you mastered this people of the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_110.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and their customs.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1100.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|nobody else did-not even Baleka,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for she was too little-and as for my father he took another young wife and was content.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_111.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|From these he heard many tales and traditions,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1110.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After that I was unhappy,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1112.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for my brothers did not love me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1113.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because I was much cleverer than they,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1115.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and was swifter in running;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1117.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so they poisoned the mind of my father against me and he treated me badly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1123.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for we were both lonely,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1124.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and she clung to me like a creeper to the only tree in a plain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1128.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and though I was young,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1129.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that to be wise is to be strong,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1132.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|yet he whose mind directs the battle is greater than he who kills.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1137.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I saw that the witch-finders and the medicine-men were feared in the land,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_114.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|are rarely told nowadays,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1141.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that everybody looked up to them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1143.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|even when they had only a stick in their hands,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1146.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|ten men armed with spears would fly before them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1149.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I learned the arts of the medicine-men.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1152.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I made sacrifices,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I did all those things of which you have heard,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1156.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I learned much;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1158.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for there is wisdom in our magic as well as lies-and you know it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_116.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in time to come may cease to be told altogether.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1162.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1163.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|else you had not come here to ask me about your lost oxen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1167.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So things went on till I was twenty years of age-a man full grown.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1172.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|By now I had mastered all I could learn by myself,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1175.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so I joined myself on to the chief medicine-man of our tribe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1179.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who was named Noma.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1180.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was old, had one eye only, and was very clever.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1184.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Of him I learned some tricks and more wisdom,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1188.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but at last he grew jealous of me and set a trap to catch me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_119.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|now that nation has been destroyed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1192.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a rich man of a neighbouring tribe had lost some cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1196.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and came with gifts to Noma praying him to smell them out.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1199.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then the headman grew angry and demanded back his gifts;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1203.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and hot words passed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1204.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, for I feared that blood would be shed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1208.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"You are nothing but a boy,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1209.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_121.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the chief aim of its white rulers is to root out the warlike spirit for which it was remarkable,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1211.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Can a boy have wisdom?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1212.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"That shall soon be known,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1214.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, taking the bones in my hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1217.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|throwing them something as we throw dice.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1219.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Leave the bones alone!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1221.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We will ask nothing more of our snakes for the good of this son of a dog.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1224.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"He shall throw the bones,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1226.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1227.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he lifted his spear.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1229.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I made haste to begin; I threw the bones.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1233.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The headman sat on the ground before me and answered my questions.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1236.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father-how sometimes the witch-doctor has knowledge of where the lost things are,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1241.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for our ears are long,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as but the other day it told me of your oxen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1246.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Well, in this case, my snake stood up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1249.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew nothing of the man's cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1251.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and told them to him one by one,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1253.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and how one of them had fallen into a stream and lay there on its back drowned,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1257.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the man was pleased,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1258.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and said that if my sight was good,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1261.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he found the cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1262.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the gifts should be taken from Noma and given to me;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1265.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he asked the people who were sitting round,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1268.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there were many,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1269.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if this was not just.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_127.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to replace it by a spirit of peaceful progress.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1270.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Yes, yes,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1271.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they said, it was just, and they would see that it was done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1275.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He knew that I had made a true divination, and he was very angry.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1280.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was a big matter:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1282.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the herd of cattle were many,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1283.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then all men would think me the greater wizard.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1286.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now it was late,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1287.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the moon had not yet risen,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1290.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After that he went away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1291.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I too went into my hut and lay down to sleep.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1295.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Suddenly I awoke, feeling a weight upon my breast.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1298.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I fell back again and looked.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_130.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|perhaps the most wonderful that the world has seen,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1300.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the moon lay low on the sky like a ball of fire far away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1304.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was seated across me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1306.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in his hand was a knife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1308.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he hissed into my ear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1310.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Very well, now I will show you how I serve such puppies.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1313.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that you cannot squeal,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1315.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I will cut you to pieces slowly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1318.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in the morning I will tell the people that the spirits did it because you lied.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1323.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Next, I will take off your arms and legs.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1325.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes, yes, I will make you like a stick!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1328.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I will
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1329.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he began driving in the knife under my chin.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_133.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|is already a thing of the past;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1332.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Mercy, my uncle,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1334.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Will you do this?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1335.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he asked, still pricking me with the knife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1337.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Will you get up,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1338.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and hide them there?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_134.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|building it up from the smallest beginnings.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1340.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he named a secret valley that was known to very few.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1343.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If you do that, I will spare you and give you three of the cows.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1348.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|by my father's spirit,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1350.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will find a way to kill you!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1352.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Certainly I will do it, my uncle,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1353.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1354.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Why did you not trust me before?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1356.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Had I known that you wanted to keep the cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1359.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would never have smelt them out.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1361.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"You are not so wicked as I thought,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1363.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Get up, then, and do my bidding.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1365.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You can be back here two hours after dawn.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1368.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I got up,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1369.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thinking all the while whether I should try to spring on him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_137.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When he appeared at the commencement of this century,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1373.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I was without arms, and he had the knife;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1376.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|also if,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1377.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I prevailed and killed him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1378.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I made another plan.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1380.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would go and find the cattle in the valley where I had smelt them out,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1384.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I would not bring them to the secret hiding-place.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1387.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1388.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and all the people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1389.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He had not been a witch-doctor till he grew old for nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1393.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He had planted me by him like a tree,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1396.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he meant to keep me clipped like a bush.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1399.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I had grown tall and overshadowed him;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_140.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it was as the ruler of a single small tribe;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1402.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went to the corner of my hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1404.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Noma watching me all the while,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1406.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I started through the moonlight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1408.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I began to run,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1410.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|singing to myself as I went,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1411.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to frighten away the ghosts,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1413.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For an hour I travelled swiftly over the plain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1416.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till I came to the hillside where the bush began.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1419.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here it was very dark under the shade of the trees,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_142.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when he fell,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1422.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I sang louder than ever.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1424.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At last I found the little buffalo path I sought, and turned along it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1429.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently I came to an open place,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_143.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in the year eighteen twenty eight,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1431.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|where the moonlight crept in between the trees.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1434.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knelt down and looked.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1436.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|sometimes whispering and sometimes talking out loud.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1440.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here the trail of the cattle was broad:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1442.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they had broken down the ferns with their feet and trampled the grass.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1446.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently I came to a pool.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1448.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And there at the edge of the pool floated the drowned ox,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_145.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as he is called also,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1453.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stepped forward and looked round.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1455.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My eye caught something;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1456.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I looked, one of them snorted, rose and shook the dew from his hide.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_146.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in his march to power he had slaughtered more than a million human beings.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1461.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He seemed big as an elephant in the mist and twilight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1464.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as Noma had bid me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1466.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I would not do this.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1468.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and tell all men that Noma was a thief.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1470.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I sat, I heard a noise, and looked up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1473.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|came a crowd of men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1475.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and leading them was Noma,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1477.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and by his side the headman who owned the cattle.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1480.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I rose and stood still, wondering;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1482.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but as I stood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1483.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they ran towards me shouting and waving sticks and spears.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1487.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|screamed Noma.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1488.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There he is!-the clever boy whom I have brought up to bring shame on me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1493.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What did I tell you?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1494.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Did I not tell you that he was a thief?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1496.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes-yes!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1497.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he is stealing the cattle!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1499.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He knew where they were all the time,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1501.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and now he is taking them away to hide them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1504.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They would be useful to buy a wife with,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1506.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my clever boy?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1507.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I understood now, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_151.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so no more need be said of them here.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1510.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My heart went mad in me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1511.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|everything began to swim round,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1513.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a red cloth seemed to lift itself up and down before my eyes.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1518.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I have always seen it thus when I was forced to fight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1521.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I screamed out one word only,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1524.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I yelled again, and rushed on at the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1526.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He got up his shield,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1528.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I knocked it down upon his head,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_153.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|has been to convey,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1530.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and over he rolled senseless.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1532.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Whether he lived or died I do not know, my father;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1535.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but his head being of the thickest, I think it likely that he lived.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in a narrative form,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1540.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while the people stood astonished,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1542.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I turned and fled like the wind.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1544.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|throwing spears at me and trying to cut me off.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1547.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went like the wind;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1549.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and presently the sound of their chase grew fainter and fainter,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_155.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to make accessible,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1553.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till at last I was out of sight and alone.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1556.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I went and hid in a patch of reeds down by a swamp.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1560.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|All day long I lay there thinking.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1562.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What was I to do?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1564.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I was a jackal without a hole.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1566.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If I went back to my people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1568.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|certainly they would kill me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_157.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in a popular shape,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1570.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whom they thought a thief.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1571.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that I did not wish,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1573.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though my heart was sad.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1575.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the boy to whom I had given the cup of water long ago.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1578.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I had heard of him: his name was known in the land;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_158.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|incidents of history which are now,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1582.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|already the air was big with it;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1584.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the very trees and grass spoke it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1586.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The words he had said and the vision that my mother had seen were beginning to come true.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1592.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that nobody could find them any more.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1594.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I thought to myself that I would arise and go to him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1598.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Perhaps he would kill me; well, what did it matter?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_16.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And when they grew weary,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_160.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|only to be found in a few scarce works of reference,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1602.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Certainly I should be killed if I stayed here.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1604.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes, I would go.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1605.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But now my heart pulled another way.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1608.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There was but one whom I loved in the world-it was my sister Baleka.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1613.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My father had betrothed her to the chief of a neighbouring tribe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1617.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I knew that this marriage was against her wish.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1620.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Perhaps my sister would run away with me if I could get near her to tell her that I was going.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1624.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would try-yes, I would try.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1627.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I waited till the darkness came down,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1630.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I was very hungry,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1631.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Some of my people were seated outside of a hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1634.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|talking together over a fire.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1636.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I crept near, silently as a snake, and hid behind a little bush.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_164.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|rarely consulted,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1641.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew that they could not see me outside the ring of the firelight,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1645.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I wanted to hear what they said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1647.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I guessed, they were talking of me and called me many names.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_165.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It will be obvious that such a task has presented difficulties,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1652.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Just then a dog that was lying by the fire got up and began to sniff the air.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1656.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I could not see what dog it was-indeed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1659.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that is what comes of want of experience, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1663.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The dog sniffed and sniffed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1665.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then he began to growl,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1666.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|looking always my way,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1668.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I grew afraid.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1669.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"What is the dog growling at?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1671.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said one man to another.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1673.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But the other man was taking snuff and did not like to move.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1676.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Let the dog go and see for himself,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1679.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he answered, sneezing,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_168.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and think with the mind and speak with the voice of a Zulu of the old regime.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1680.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"what is the good of keeping a dog if you have to catch the thief?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1683.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the first man to the dog.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1685.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he ran forward, barking.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1687.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as I lay not knowing what to do,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1690.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|stopped barking,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1691.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I whispered to him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1692.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he lay down by my side.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1694.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Where has that dog gone now?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1696.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the first man.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1698.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that he stops barking suddenly and does not come back?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_17.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|did you not stand and say,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1700.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"We will see,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1701.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the other, rising, a spear in his hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1705.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now once more I was terribly afraid,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1708.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|or I must run for my life again.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1710.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But as I sprang up to run,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1712.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a big black snake glided between the men and went off towards the huts.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1717.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They jumped aside in a great fright,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1719.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then all of them turned to follow the snake,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1722.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|saying that this was what the dog was barking at.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1725.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1726.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which without any doubt took the shape of a snake to save my life.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_173.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|their details have, therefore, been suppressed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1731.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At first I thought that I would kill him, lest he should betray me;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1735.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he sat down upon the ground wagging his tail,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1738.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I thought that I would take my chance, and we went on together.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1742.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|This was my purpose:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1744.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|would be empty,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1745.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I came to the reed fence that surrounded the huts.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1748.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Nobody was to be seen at the gate,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_175.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Still much remains,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1750.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which was not shut with thorns as usual.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1753.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was my duty to close it, and I had not been there to do so.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1757.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bidding the dog lie down outside,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1759.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stepped through boldly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1761.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|reached the door of my hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1763.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and listened.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1764.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was empty; there was not even a breath to be heard.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1767.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which was so nicely carved that I did not like to leave it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_177.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|may be invited to leave this book unread.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1771.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Soon I found them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1773.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I felt about for my skin rug,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1775.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and as I did so my hand touched something cold.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1779.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I started, and felt again.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1781.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was a man's face-the face of a dead man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1785.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I was frightened,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1786.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when suddenly I heard the voices of women talking outside the door of the hut.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_179.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|indeed nearly all,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1791.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew the voices;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1792.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I was in a trap indeed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1794.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently she was in,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1796.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she began to make lamentations and to call down curses on me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1801.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she did not know that I was listening.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1803.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now that the woman was there I was not so much afraid of the dead man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1807.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that he had been a great cheat;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1809.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so I thought I would make him cheat for the last time.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_181.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for the reason given,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1813.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I placed my hands beneath his shoulders and pushed him up so that he sat upon the ground.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1818.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The woman heard the noise and made a sound in her throat.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_182.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that he prophesied of the coming of the white man after receiving his death wounds.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1822.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Can you not let me be at peace, even now when I am dead?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1826.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|drew in her breath to shriek aloud.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1829.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I must teach you silence.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1831.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then her senses left her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1833.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and whether she ever found them again I do not know.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1836.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At least she grew quiet for that time.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1839.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and worth three oxen-and I fled,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1842.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1843.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|was two hundred paces away,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1845.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I must go thither,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1846.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because a man was always on guard there.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1849.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew on which side of the hut it was her custom to lie,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1852.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and where her head would be.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1854.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I lay down on my side and gently,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1857.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|began to bore a hole in the grass covering of the hut.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1860.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It took a long while,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1862.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for the thatch was thick,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1863.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but at last I was nearly through it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1866.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for it came into my mind that Baleka might have changed her place,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_187.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it is impossible to speak so certainly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1870.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that I might wake the wrong girl.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1872.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I almost gave it over,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1874.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thinking that I would fly alone,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1876.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when suddenly I heard a girl wake and begin to cry on the other side of the thatch.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1880.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"that is Baleka, who weeps for her brother!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1883.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I put my lips where the thatch was thinnest and whispered:-
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1887.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Say not a word, but rise.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1889.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Come out of the hut, bringing your skin blanket.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_189.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he cannot discover any confirmation of it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1892.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she did not shriek, as most girls would have done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1895.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she understood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1896.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she rose and crept from the hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1898.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|her blanket in her hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_19.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|pointing towards the ocean:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1900.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she whispered, as we met.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1901.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Surely you will be killed!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1903.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And then I told her of the plan which I had made.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1906.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Will you come with me?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1907.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, when I had done,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1909.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She thought awhile, then she said,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1912.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I love you alone among our people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1915.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though I believe that this will be the end of it-that you will lead me to my death.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1919.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I did not think much of her words at the time,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_192.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|these kings undoubtedly put their soldiers to many tests of equal severity.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1922.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but afterwards they came back to me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1925.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we slipped away together,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1927.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as we were afraid of being seen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1929.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Towards the afternoon we heard voices,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1931.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1932.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At night we travelled again;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1934.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we were met by an old woman,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1936.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who looked oddly at us but said nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1938.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After that we pushed on day and night,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1941.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for we knew that the old woman would tell the pursuers if she met them;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1945.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and so indeed it came about.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1947.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and saw that they had been trampled down.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1949.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Among the broken mealies we found the body of a very old man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1953.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We wondered at this, and went on a little way.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1956.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Afterwards we became used to such sights.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1959.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|scores of them-old men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_196.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Umbopo, or Mopo, as he is named in this tale, actually lived.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1961.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|young men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1962.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|little babies at the breast-there they lay among the burnt huts,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1966.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Red was the earth with their blood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1968.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and red they looked in the red light of the setting sun.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1972.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was as though all the land had been smeared with the bloody hand of the Great Spirit,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1977.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Baleka saw it and began to cry;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1980.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she was weary,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1981.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|poor girl,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1982.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we had found little to eat,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1984.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|only grass and green corn.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1986.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"An enemy has been here,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1987.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and as I spoke I thought that I heard a groan from the other side of a broken reed hedge.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1992.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went and looked.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1994.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There lay a young woman:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1995.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she was badly wounded, but still alive, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_1999.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|A little way from her lay a man dead,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you knew his brother Panda and his captains,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_20.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Kill me if you wish,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2001.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and before him several other men of another tribe:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2004.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he had died fighting.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2006.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|another, a little one, lay on her body.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2009.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I looked at the woman,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_201.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then he disappears from the scene,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2010.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she groaned again,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2011.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|opened her eyes and saw me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2013.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that I had a spear in my hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2016.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Kill me quickly!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2017.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2018.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Have you not tortured me enough?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2020.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said that I was a stranger and did not want to kill her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2023.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Then bring me water,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2025.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There were bodies in it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2027.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I dragged them out,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2028.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and her strength came back a little-the water gave her life.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_203.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but it is not accurately known whether he also went
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2032.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"How did you come to this?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2033.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2034.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes, I woke up to hear the sound of killing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2037.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I was sleeping by my husband,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2039.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with him who lies there,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2040.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the children.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2042.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We all ran out.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2043.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My husband had a spear and shield.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2045.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was a brave man.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2046.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he died bravely:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2048.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he killed three of the Zulu devils before he himself was dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2052.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and stabbed me till they thought that I was dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2054.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Afterwards, they went away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2056.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She stopped, gave a great cry, and died.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_206.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which has been considerably varied to suit the purposes of this romance.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2060.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My sister wept at the sight, and I too was stirred by it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2064.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I thought to myself,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2065.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If he is not evil such things would not happen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2068.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|That is how I thought then, my father; now I think differently.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2072.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I know that we had not found out the path of the Great Spirit,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2076.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that is all.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2077.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I was a chicken in those days, my father;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2080.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|afterwards I got used to such sights.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2082.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we had to look at the water to see if it was clean before we drank.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2086.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|People learned how to die then and not make a noise about it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2091.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What does it matter?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2092.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They would have been dead now anyway.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2094.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It does not matter; nothing matters, except being born.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2098.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|That is a mistake, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_210.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Among the Zulus and Amatongas.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2100.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but we could not sleep,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2102.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the ghosts of the dead people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|moving about and calling to each other.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2106.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was natural that they should do so;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2109.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|men were looking for their wives, and mothers for their children.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2112.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But we were afraid that they might be angry with us for being there,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2116.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so we clung together and trembled in each other's arms.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2119.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and towards morning their cries grew fainter.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_212.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I heard a story the other day,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2122.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When the first light came we rose and picked our way through the dead down to the plain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2127.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and sometimes we came to the body of a warrior who had been killed because his wounds prevented him from marching farther.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_213.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he says,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2134.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for after what we had seen I grew afraid lest he should kill us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2138.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we had nowhere to turn,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2139.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so I said that we would walk along till something happened.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_214.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I might have worked up into a first-class sensational novel.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2143.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now we grew faint with hunger and weariness,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2145.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for then there would be no more trouble.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2147.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we sat down by a spring.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2149.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I did not wish to die yet,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2151.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and it would have been well to do so.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and presently I heard him spring at something and the sound of struggling.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2158.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as big as himself,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2159.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that was asleep in it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2161.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for here was food.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2162.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we took bits of the flesh,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2164.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for we had no fire to cook them with.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2166.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is not nice to eat uncooked flesh,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2169.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but we were so hungry that we did not mind,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2172.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the food refreshed us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2174.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When we had eaten what we could,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2176.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we rose and washed ourselves at the spring;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2179.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|on the crest of the hill,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_218.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is the story that has been woven into the plot of this book.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2180.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|about ten spear-throws away,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2183.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|was a party of six armed men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2185.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|people of my own tribe-children of my father Makedama-who still pursued us to take us or kill us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2192.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They saw us-they raised a shout, and began to run.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2196.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now the land lay thus.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2197.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which twisted through the plain like a great and shining snake.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_22.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I tell you that for every drop of my blood a hundred avengers shall rise from yonder sea!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2201.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|On the other side the ground rose again,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2204.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we did not know what was beyond,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2206.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We ran for the river-where else were we to run?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2209.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And after us came the warriors.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2211.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They gained on us;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2212.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they were strong, and they were angry because they had come so far.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2216.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Run as we would, still they gained.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2218.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now we neared the banks of the river; it was full and wide.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_222.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it was told to Mister Leslie by the Zulu who performed the feat and thereby won a wife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2222.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Above us the waters ran angrily,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2224.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|between the two a deep pool,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2227.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|where the water was quiet but the stream strong.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2230.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my brother, what shall we do?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2231.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"There is this to choose,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2233.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2234.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|perish on the spears of our people or try the river.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2237.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Easier to die by water than on iron,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2240.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2241.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now may our snakes look towards us and the spirits of our fathers be with us!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2245.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At the least we can swim.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2247.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And I led her to the head of the pool.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2249.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which I held in my teeth-and we plunged in,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2252.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|wading as far as we could.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2254.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now we were up to our breasts;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2256.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|now we had lost the earth and were swimming towards the middle of the river,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2260.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you swim, do you?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2261.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Well, you will drown;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2262.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if we must run over the edge of the world after you we will catch you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2266.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which fell between us like a flash of light.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2269.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|While he spoke we swam hard, and now we were in the current.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_227.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Also the writer's thanks are due to his friends,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2273.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It swept us downwards, but still we made way, for we could swim well.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2278.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was just this:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2279.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if we could reach the bank before we were swept into the rapids we were safe;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2284.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if not, then-good night!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2286.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now we were near the other side, but, alas!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2289.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we were also near the lip of the foaming water.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_229.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|late Zulu border agent,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2292.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We strained, we struggled.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2294.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Baleka was a brave girl, and she swam bravely;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2298.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but the water pushed her down below me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2300.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I could do nothing to help her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2302.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I could not go back.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2303.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She grasped him by the tail with her right hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2306.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then he put out his strength-he was very strong.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_231.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for much information given to him in bygone years by word of mouth,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2310.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She too struck out with her feet and left hand,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2313.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and slowly-very slowly-drew near.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2316.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She caught it with her left hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2318.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Already her feet were over the brink of the rapids,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2321.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we brought her safe into the shallows,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2324.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and from the shallows to the bank,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2326.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there she fell gasping.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2328.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now when the soldiers on the other bank saw that we had crossed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2332.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they shouted threats at us,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2334.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then ran away down the bank.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2335.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2336.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Ah, let me die!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2337.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2339.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For two hours we walked,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2340.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till at last we came to the crest of the rise,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2343.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2344.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Yes, brother,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2345.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2346.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but what waits us there?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2347.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Death is behind us and before us-we are in the middle of death.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_235.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|formerly treasurer to the Government of Natal,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2352.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then we looked back, and lo!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2354.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Again we ran, but now we were weak, and they gained upon us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2358.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then once more I thought of the dog.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2360.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was fierce and would tear any one on whom I set him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2364.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I called him and told him what to do,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2366.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He understood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2367.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and flew towards the soldiers growling,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2369.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his hair standing up on his spine.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2372.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he jumped round them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2373.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At last a man hit him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2375.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he sprang up and seized the man by the throat.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2378.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There he clung,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2379.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|man and dog rolling over and over together,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_238.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whose compilation,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2383.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till the end of it was that they both died.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2386.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he was a dog!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2387.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We do not see such dogs nowadays.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2389.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Meanwhile, we had been running.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_239.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"The Annals of Natal,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2391.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there was something going on inside it;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2394.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|leaving the dead dog and the dying man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2396.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|came after us swiftly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2397.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I saw that they must catch us before we reached the gate,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_240.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Watcher of the Fords,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2401.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then a thought came into my head.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2403.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I had brought her here, I would save her life if I could.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2406.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, dropping behind.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2408.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now she was almost blind with weariness and terror,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2411.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I was about to fight four men till I was killed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2415.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and all fear left me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2417.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The men were running,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2418.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|two and two,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2419.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with the length of a spear throw between them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_242.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|is an historical weapon,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2422.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But of the first pair one was five or six paces in front of the other.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2427.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|This man shouted out loud and charged me, shield and spear up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was an arbitrary person, for
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2431.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I was crafty and he was overbold.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2434.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|On he came.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2435.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stood waiting for him till he drew back the spear to stab me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2439.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then suddenly I dropped to my knees and thrust upward with all my strength,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2444.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|beneath the rim of his shield,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2446.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he also thrust,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2447.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but over me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2448.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his spear only cutting the flesh of my shoulder-see!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2453.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|here is its scar; yes, to this day.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2456.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it went home; it ran through and through his middle.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_246.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|no matter what was discussed in our village,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2460.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He rolled over and over on the plain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2462.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The dust hid him;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2464.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|leaving nothing but a little bit of stick in my hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2466.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then in the darkness I saw a light.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2469.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I fell on to my hands and knees and flung myself over sideways.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2474.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|lifting his feet from beneath him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2476.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Down he came heavily.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2478.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Before he had touched the ground I was off it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_248.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he would bring it to a conclusion with a stick.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2480.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|His spear had fallen from his hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2483.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stooped, seized it, and as he rose I stabbed him through the back.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2488.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was all done in the shake of a leaf, my father;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2491.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in the shake of a leaf he also was dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2494.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|About a hundred paces from me Baleka was staggering along with her arms out like one who has drunk too much beer.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_250.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But he made a good end;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2502.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But then her strength left her altogether.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2504.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2505.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|there she fell senseless, and I stood by her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2509.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I should have been killed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2510.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|had not this chanced,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2511.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|since the other two men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2513.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|having stayed one instant by their dead fellows,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2516.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and through it ran a party of soldiers dragging a prisoner by the arms.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_252.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for when the Zulu soldiers attacked him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2521.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After them walked a great man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2523.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who wore a leopard skin on his shoulders,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2526.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and was laughing,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2527.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and after them again came a company of warriors.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2530.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"We are of the children of Makedama,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2532.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but now two of us are dead at their hands,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2534.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and others lie dead along the road.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2536.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Suffer that we slay them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2538.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the soldiers;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2539.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|ask too that he suffer you should not be slain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_254.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he killed no less than twenty of them with the Watcher,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2542.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Just then the tall chief saw blood and heard words.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2546.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He stalked up;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2548.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and his chest was big as the chests of two;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2551.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his face was fierce and beautiful,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2553.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he asked, frowning.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2555.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the captain of the soldiers,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2557.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bending himself double before him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2559.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2560.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said those men of my people who sought to kill us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2563.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he answered, then spoke once more to the captain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2567.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|let themselves be blinded and turned loose to seek their way home,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_257.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the spears stuck in him
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2572.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because they have dared to lift a spear within the Zulu gates.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2576.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now praise on, my children!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2578.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while the soldiers murmured,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_258.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as thick as reeds in a morass.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2580.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his justice is bright and terrible like the sun! But the two men of my people cried out in fear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2587.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Cut out their tongues also,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2589.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There lies the girl.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2590.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She is asleep and helpless.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2592.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you hesitate?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2593.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Take these men, smear them with honey, and pin them over ant-heaps;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2598.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But first kill these two hunted jackals,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_260.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|This man's strength was so great that he could kill a leopard
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2601.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They seem tired and doubtless they long for sleep.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2605.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then for the first time I spoke, for the soldiers drew near to slay us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2609.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I broke in,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2610.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was I who gave thee a gourd of water many years ago,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2614.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when we were both little.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2615.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|vowing that thou wouldst protect me and never do me harm.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2619.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I have come, bringing my sister with me;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2622.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and now, I pray thee, do not eat up the words of long ago.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2625.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I spoke,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2627.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he listened earnestly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2628.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2629.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Welcome, Mopo!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2630.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But of thy sister I said nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2633.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|should she not be slain when I swore vengeance against all thy tribe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2637.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|save thee alone?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2638.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered, boldly;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_264.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with his hands only,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2640.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"also because I love her, and ask her life as a boon!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2644.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And they did so, showing her face.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2646.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the chief.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2647.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I grant thee the boon.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2649.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I sat down and told him all.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_265.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It has been little if at all exaggerated.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2651.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Nor did he grow weary of listening.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2654.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when I had done,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2655.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if he had still been alive,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2657.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then he spoke to the captain of the soldiers.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2659.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I take back my words,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2661.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2662.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|One shall die and the other shall go free.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2665.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|here, Mopo, we have a man who has proved himself a coward.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2669.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The man fought well-he slew three of my people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2673.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then this dog was afraid to meet him face to face.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2677.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and afterwards he stabbed the woman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2679.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I will do him honour.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_268.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to take the form of a young maiden,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2681.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will send back the other pig to the sty with a message.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2685.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Choose, children of Makedama, which of you will live.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2688.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now the two men of my tribe were brothers,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2691.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and loved one another,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2692.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and each of them was willing to die that the other might go free.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2696.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|saying that they would fight the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2698.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"What, is there honour among pigs?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_27.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_270.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in fact an angel.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2701.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I will settle it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2702.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I throw it into the air;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2704.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if the blade falls uppermost the tall man shall go free;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2708.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if the shaft falls uppermost, then life is to the short one, so!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_271.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She is said to appear to some chosen person,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2713.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he sent the little spear whirling round and round in the air.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2717.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Every eye watched it as it wheeled and fell.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2720.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The haft struck the ground first.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2722.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and say to him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2724.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|To-day the dog of thy son Mopo howls upon the roof of thy hut.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2729.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The saying conveyed a threat to be appreciated by every Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2733.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|shook his brother by the hand,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2734.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bearing the words of evil omen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2737.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bidding them fight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2738.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when they had praised the prince they fought fiercely,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_274.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to whom she imparts some revelation;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2742.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the end of it was that the man of my people conquered the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2746.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But as soon as he had found his breath again he was set to run for his life,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2751.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and after him ran five chosen men.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2754.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it came about that he outran them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2756.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I think that he bade the men who hunted him to make speed slowly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_276.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whatever that revelation may be,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2761.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that he would always save the life of a brave man if he could do so without making his word nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2768.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And for my part,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2769.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|were the events that ended in the coming of me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2772.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which is as are other tales of our people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2775.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But that shall be seen,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2777.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for from these matters,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2778.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|of whose love my story has to tell.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_278.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it is kept a profound secret from outsiders.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2781.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though few knew it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2782.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and had her beauty again,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2783.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|numbering her among his women,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2785.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he was so well pleased with my medicine that in the end I became his head doctor.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2791.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now this was a great post,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2792.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|during the course of years,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2794.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I grew fat in cattle and in wives;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2796.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but also it was one of much danger.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2799.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For when I rose strong and well in the morning,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_28.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so it was told me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2802.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I could never know but that at night I should sleep stiff and red.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2806.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|doctored they never so well, they were killed at last.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_281.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|just before the Zulu war,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2810.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For a day would surely come when the king felt ill in his body or heavy in his mind,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2815.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yet I escaped,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2817.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because of the power of my medicine,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2819.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So it came about that where the king went there I went with him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2823.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I slept near his hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2825.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I sat behind him at council,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2827.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in the battle I was ever at his side.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_283.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|revealing something or other which had a great effect throughout the land,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2830.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the battle!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2831.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|In those days we knew how to fight, my father!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2834.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the hyenas would steal along our path in packs,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2837.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and none went empty away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2839.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|now for the first time armed with the short stabbing-spear.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2842.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|there were seventeen of them;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2844.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the earth was black with their number;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2846.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|were on a hill,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2847.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and between us lay a valley down which there ran a little stream.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2851.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the regiments arose from their bed of spears;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2854.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they sprang up and shook the dew from hair and shield-yes!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2858.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There was the breast of spears,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_286.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I know that the Zulus were quite impressed that some calamity was about to befall them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2860.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|there were the horns of spears,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2862.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they were numberless as the stars,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2864.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and like the stars they shone.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2866.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|their plumes bent in the breeze;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2868.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|like a plain of seeding grass they bent,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2870.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they laughed in the joy of the waking of battle.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2873.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Was it not well to die on the spear?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2875.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Was it not well to die for the king?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2878.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Death was the arms of Victory.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2880.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|her breast is fair.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2881.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the music of which has the power to drive men mad,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2885.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|rose far away to the left,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2887.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We are the Zulu, children of the Lion, What!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2891.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|did you tremble?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2892.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|followed by his captains,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2894.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He walked along like a great buck;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2896.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|death was in his eyes,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2897.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|only the sound of chanting still rolled along the hills.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_29.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the regiments turned staring towards the Black Water,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2901.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he shouted, and his voice was like the voice of a bull.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2905.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Yonder, father,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2906.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the regiments.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2907.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And every spear pointed across the valley.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2910.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"They do not come,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2911.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he shouted again.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2913.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Shall we then sit here till we grow old?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2915.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"No, father,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2916.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2917.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|begin!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2918.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he shouted a third time,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_292.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|One of the ominous signs was that fire is said to have descended from heaven,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2920.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Go, my children!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2921.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There is the foe.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2923.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Go and return no more!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2925.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"We hear you, father!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2926.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they answered with one voice,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2928.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and moved down the slope like a countless herd of game with horns of steel.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2933.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|lines of light played above his spears.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2936.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Hearken to the song of battle!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2938.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|To and fro they swing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2940.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They pour back across the stream-half of them; the rest are dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2944.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|two more run to the right,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2946.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and yet another two to the left.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2948.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Again comes the roar of the meeting shields.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2951.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|these are men: they fight, they do not run.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2954.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They fall by hundreds and by thousands,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2957.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but no man shows his back,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2959.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and on each man there lie two dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_296.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and ignited the grass over the graves of the former kings of Zululand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2962.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Wow! my father, of those two regiments not one escaped.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2968.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now there are no such men.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2969.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They are all dead and quiet.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2971.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|spears are shining among the trees.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2973.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now the horns of our host close upon the flanks of the foe.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2977.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They slay and are slain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2979.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the battle turns against us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2981.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It has come at last.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2983.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Children of the Zulu!  There is a roar,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2986.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a thunder of feet,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2988.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a flashing of spears,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2989.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a bending of plumes,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2991.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|like storm-clouds before the gale,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2993.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we sweep down upon friend and foe.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2996.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They form up to meet us;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_2998.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We trample them down.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_300.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that the native women buried their young children up to their heads in sand,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3000.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What matter?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3001.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They can fight no more.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3002.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Everything grows red.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3004.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We swept them away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3005.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but the hillside was black and red.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3008.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Few fled; few were left to fly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3011.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We passed over them like fire; we ate them up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3015.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently we paused, looking for the foe.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3017.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|All were dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3019.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then we mustered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3020.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Ten regiments had looked upon the morning sun;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3023.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will tell you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3024.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He spoke to them gently, gently.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3027.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He thanked them for their service.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3029.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What then was there now left for him to do?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3032.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he covered his face with his blanket.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3034.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then the soldiers killed them all,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3037.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|That is how we dealt with cowards in those days, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_304.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|deserting them for the time being,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3041.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If ten came against him, still he did not turn his back.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3045.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Fight and fall, but fly not,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3047.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|That fight was but one war out of many.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3050.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but with victory and countless cattle.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3053.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Tribe after tribe went down before us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3056.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|yet the army grew.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3058.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Soon there were no other chiefs left.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_306.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|going away weeping,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3060.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then we poured into this land of Natal.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3063.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When we entered, its people could not be numbered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3066.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Men, women, and children, we wiped them out;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_307.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For this divine personage there is,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3070.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the land was clean of them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3072.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And so it went on and on,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3074.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that he would have no children,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3076.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Every child born to him by his
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3078.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|was put away at once.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3079.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"What, Mopo,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3081.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he said to me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3082.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They die at the hands of those whom they have bred.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3085.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will rule for my life,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3086.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my sister Baleka,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3088.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the king's wife,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3089.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|fell in labour;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_309.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the same may be said of most of the supernatural matters spoken of in these pages.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3090.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and this but eight days after my second wife,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3093.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|had given birth to a son.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3095.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|saying it was well that a doctor should know the sicknesses of women and learn how to cure their evil tempers.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3102.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As though, my father, that were possible!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because he loved her a little,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3106.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|commanding me to attend her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3108.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and when the child was born to cause its body to be brought to him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3112.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|according to custom,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3114.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that he might be sure that it was dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3116.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and would not her child be of my own blood?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3119.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it must be so,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3120.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if we dared to disobey,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3122.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Better that an infant should die than that we should become food for jackals.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3127.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the place of the king's wives,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3129.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but when they saw me they rose and went away,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3132.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for it was not lawful that they should stay where I was.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3136.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Thus I was left alone with my sister.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3138.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I did not speak,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_314.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Briefly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3140.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though I saw by the heaving of her breast that she was weeping.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3144.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said at length;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3145.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|your sorrow will soon be done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3147.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered, lifting her head,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3149.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it will be but begun.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_315.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|or the spirit of an ancestor,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3151.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Oh, cruel man!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3152.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I know the reason of your coming.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You come to murder the babe that shall be born of me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3157.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is the king's word, woman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3159.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is the king's word, and what is the king's word?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_316.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to that of a god.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3161.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Have I, then, naught to say in this matter?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3164.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Have I not loved you, Mopo?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3166.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Did I not flee with you from our people and the vengeance of our father?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3170.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and would have caused you to be slain had I not pleaded for you and called his oath to mind?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3175.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And thus you pay me: you come to kill my child, my first-born child!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_318.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|In the case of an able and highly intelligent person like the Mopo of this story,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3180.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"It is the king's word, woman,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3182.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|turning her face to the wall of the hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3184.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she wept and groaned bitterly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3187.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as she wept I heard a stir without the hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3190.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the light in the doorway was darkened.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3193.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I looked round to see who it was,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3195.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then fell upon the ground in salutation,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3198.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|mother of the king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3199.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Mother of the Heavens,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_32.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|your name became great among the people of the Zulu,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3200.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that same lady to whom my mother had refused the milk.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3204.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Greeting, Mopo,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3205.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3206.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Is it because the sorrow of women is upon her?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3209.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|mother of a king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3210.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because this man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3211.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who is my brother,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3213.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|has come from him who is my lord and thy son,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3216.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to murder that which shall be born of me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3218.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|O thou whose breasts have given suck, plead for me!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_322.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the ideal would probably not be a low one;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3222.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Thy son was not slain at birth.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3225.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Mother of the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3226.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yet may his child be otherwise, Mother of the Heavens!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3229.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Think, thou hast no grandson to comfort thee in thy age.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3233.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The king, our lord, lives in war.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3235.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He too may die, and what then?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3237.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Has the king no brothers?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3239.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They are not of thy flesh, mother.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3241.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thou dost not hearken!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then as a woman to woman I plead with thee.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3246.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Save my child or slay me with my child!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3249.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"How may this be done, Mopo?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_325.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It only remains to the writer to express his regret that this story is not more varied in its hue.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3251.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and even reeds have ears,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3253.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Are there then no other new-born babes in Zululand?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3256.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|sitting up and speaking in a whisper like the hiss of a snake.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3260.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Listen, Mopo!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3261.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Is not your wife also in labour?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3263.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now hear me, Mother of the Heavens, and, my brother, hear me also.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3267.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Do not think to play with me in this matter.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3270.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For I will tell the king that you came to me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3272.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then Unandi spoke.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3274.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and swear that you will be faithful to me in this secret,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3277.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as I swear to you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3279.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and then in reward you shall be the greatest of the people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3282.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the king's voice,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3284.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whisperer in the king's ear.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3285.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I swear, Mother of the Heavens,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3287.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3288.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"It is well, my brother,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3290.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now go and do that which must be done swiftly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3293.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for my sorrow is upon me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3294.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|knowing that if you fail I will be pitiless,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3297.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I will bring you to your death,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3299.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|yes,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3300.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|even if my own death is the price!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3302.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I went.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3303.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Whither do you go?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3304.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|asked the guard at the gate.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3306.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I go to bring my medicines, men of the king,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3308.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I said; but, oh!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_331.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It would have been desirable to introduce some gayer and more happy incidents.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3310.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my heart was heavy, and this was my plan-to fly far from Zululand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3316.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I could not, and I dared not do this thing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3318.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|saving the child to look upon the sun which he had doomed to darkness?
