/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3324.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|leaving all,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3325.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and seek out some far tribe where I might begin to live again.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3329.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here I could not live;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3331.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I reached my own huts,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3333.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she who eight days gone had borne me a son.
