/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3342.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she who lived to be Nada the Beautiful,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3345.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then a thought came into my heart.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3347.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here was a path to run on.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3349.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Give me the boy,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_335.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But it has not been possible.
