/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3351.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He is not dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3352.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"It is of no use-the child is dead,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3355.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Give him to me, woman!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3356.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said fiercely.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3358.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And she gave me the body.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3360.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I took him and wrapped him up in my bundle of medicines,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3363.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Suffer none to enter the hut till I return,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3366.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and speak no word of the child that seems to be dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3369.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If you allow any to enter,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_337.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is believed that the picture given of the times is a faithful one,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3371.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|or if you speak a word,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3372.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then my medicine will not work and the babe will be dead indeed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3376.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I went,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3377.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|leaving the women wondering,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3378.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for it is not our custom to save both when twins are born;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3382.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I bring the medicines, men of the king!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3385.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3386.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"The child is born,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3387.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the mother of the king.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3389.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she whispered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3390.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I loosed the mat and drew the dead child from the medicines,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3393.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|glancing round fearfully as I did so.
