/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3397.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I whispered back.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3398.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They gave it to me and I took of a drug that I knew and rubbed it on the tongue of the child.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_340.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though it may be open to correction in some of its details.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3404.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But round the throat of the still-born babe I tied a string of fibre as though I had strangled it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3411.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and wrapped it loosely in a piece of matting.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3414.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now for the first time I spoke to Baleka:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3417.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Mother of the Heavens,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3419.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I have done your wish,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3420.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but know that before all is finished this deed shall bring about the death of many.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3425.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went again,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3426.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|showing them that which was in it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3428.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but saying nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3429.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they said, nodding.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3431.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But now ill-fortune found me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3433.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that is the royal house, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3435.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Good!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3436.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will come now;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3437.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here is that which the king seeks,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3439.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I showed them the dead child.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_344.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the aged man who tells the tale of his wrongs and vengeance could not be expected to treat his subject in an optimistic or even in a cheerful vein.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_3441.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Take it to him if you will.
