/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5643.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5644.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The king's will be done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5646.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the soldier;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5647.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you must live yourself,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5648.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The king's will be done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_565.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and every afternoon he came and talked with him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5650.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The sun is hot, and I tire of the road.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5652.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Thus I spoke, my father, and, indeed, in that hour I desired to die.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5658.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The world was empty for me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5660.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and my other wives and children were murdered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5662.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I had no heart to begin to build up a new house,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5665.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|none were left for me to love,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5667.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and it seemed well that I should die also.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5670.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They said, Yes, it was true.
