/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5675.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I wondered at this,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5677.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I thought that they would kill me where I stood.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5679.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we went on,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_568.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|sitting far into the night.
