/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5695.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with the shaft of the royal red wood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5697.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the son of Baleka,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5699.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|according to their custom,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_57.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it will be forgotten,
