/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_572.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then the old man told him the tale that is set out here.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5722.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But he smiled grimly, and bade them be seated.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5725.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then he spoke to them, saying,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5727.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will tell you:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5728.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it is because he is away upon my business,
