/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5733.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I am come to cure her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5734.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Thus he spoke,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5736.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|eyeing them as he did so,
