/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5750.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is pleasant,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5751.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to see you kissing yonder child.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5753.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who lay asleep,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5754.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|might not wake and utter foolish words in her wandering.
