/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5768.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Kiss him, Mother of the Heavens, kiss him!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5771.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Whom do they call him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5772.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the young cub who brings ill-fortune to our doors?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5775.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And she laughed wildly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5777.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and sank back upon the bed of skins.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5779.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"They call him the son of Mopo and Macropha,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_578.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is not all written in these pages,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5782.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the king in a low voice.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5784.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Whose son is he, then, woman?"
