/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_58.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Only your name will not be forgotten;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_580.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Was the death of a warrior in question,
