/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5816.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|palmed off upon this house to bring a curse on it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5819.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and whom she would lead out before the people when the land is weary of the wickedness of the king,
