/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_5839.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Thou wouldst give me a son to slay me and rule in my place;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/3hours/6097_584.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|showing how the blow fell and where;
